        ": سُئِلَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنِ اَلْمُتْعَةِ أَ هِيَ مِنَ اَلْأَرْبَعِ قَالَ \"لاَ وَ لاَ مِنَ اَلسَّبْعِينَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4594 - Hammad narrated from Abu Basir, who said:\nAbu Abdillah (as) was asked about Mutah (temporary marriage) - whether it is counted as part of the four [wives].\nImam (as) said: \"No, and not even among seventy.\""
        ]
      }
